<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1446286-is-this-the-best-book-about-civil-war">Is this the best book about civil war?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1446286'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F44236.The_Civil_War_Vol_1">like</a></span>

