<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link962687" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=962687&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1446286-is-this-the-best-book-about-civil-war%2Fanswers%2F962687-it-s-definitely-not">flag</a>
</div>
