<span id="freeTextContainer16910999417753214660">Shelby Foote has earned his sobriquet, &quot;American Homer&quot;, for the is the Bard of the American Civil War. Reading him is like watching <i>Gettysburg</i>. All you want to do is to join the sparkling mass of bayonets, marching off into those sunny fields of valor.</span>
  <span id="freeText16910999417753214660" style="display:none">Shelby Foote has earned his sobriquet, "American Homer", for the is the Bard of the American Civil War. Reading him is like watching <i>Gettysburg</i>. All you want to do is to join the sparkling mass of bayonets, marching off into those sunny fields of valor.</span>
